Recommendation to authorize City Manager, or designee, to execute the necessary documents to amend Contract No. 34242 with Plenary Properties Long Beach, LLC, of Los Angeles, CA, for Civic Center technology infrastructure, in an amount not to exceed $7,050,000;	

Authorize City Manager, or designee, to execute multiple lease-purchase agreements, and related financing documents, with Banc of America Public Capital Corporation, of Scottsdale, AZ, for the financing of Civic Center technology infrastructure, in an aggregate amount not to exceed $8,476,000 including principal, interest, and escrow fees, payable over a term not to exceed 15 years; and

Increase appropriations in the General Services Fund (IS 385) in the Technology and Innovation Department (TI) by $454,000, offset by charges to user departments and funds.  (Citywide)
